---
title: Creamy Chicken Caesar Lettuce Wraps with Parmesan & Croutons
description: All hail this low-carb, quick-to-the-table lunch idea! It’s light, creamy, and full of texture, flavor, and crunch. You’ll dice up tender pre-cooked chicken and combine it with crispy croutons, Parm, and chopped lettuce, then dress it in a creamy, savory Caesar dressing and wrap it in baby romaine lettuce leaves. It’s a lunchtime coup the likes of which Brutus would be proud.
